column5: Well I finally got out fishing we hit the eyes first got three nice ones all around 20" range. 2 big cats one was 30" the other 25" and the other two were around 20" some rockies and a sm. Sorry team 4 no pics I did not have my sign in the boat  We put in 1 1/2 hours musky fishing and got two small guys around 30-36" it was great to be out on the water before the fog rolled in and leave before it got way to hot.  Next time I will bring the camera.
Either way, you had a great day of fishing I will see about busting this 30 inch fish thing thats going on, go team 4
